<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7468> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7468" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Praetor of uncertain date but as addressee of the autobiography of M. Aemilius Scaurus should be dated to the late second or early first century (Plin. NH 33.21; Wiseman, NM 232, no. 183; Sumner, Orators 70). Perhaps identifiable with RE no. 4, but more probably his father. See MRR 2.76 and 81.\n" .
